{"tid":1824046,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"其實習總真係好有文化","createTime":"2020-01-14T07:08:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-14T08:46:45.000Z","uid":90166,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ce2cc9196d8bb9d8e19ac7d77d68f21af3aa06dd","tid":1824046,"uid":90166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T07:08:48.000Z","msg":"有一个周末，我去给近平同志送材料，之后闲聊了几句，就聊到了读书和学习。我问他：&lsquo;你在延安插队时都看什么书？&rsquo;他说：&lsquo;我跟你说我看过什么书，你相信吗？&rsquo;我说：&lsquo;我相信。&rsquo;他说：&lsquo;我背过《新华字典》。&rsquo;我听后，大吃一惊。近平同志的文化底蕴，不仅仅是通过博览群书，也是通过刻苦勤奋的学习不断积累起来的。一个十五六岁的少年，在黄土高原上一页一页地背厚厚的《新华字典》，他是为了把汉字读懂，读懂了汉字，之后才能更好地读懂博大的中国文化。今天，我们看近平同志用典，可以说是信手拈来，随口而出，用得恰到好处，既不是炫技，也不是&lsquo;掉书袋&rsquo;。这都是基于他对中国文化知根知底的了解。&rdquo;<br />\n<a href=\"http://cpc.people.com.cn/n1/2020/0110/c64387-31542997.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcpc.people.com.cn%2Fn1%2F2020%2F0110%2Fc64387-31542997.html&d=RrW1hT%2ByM3GEQeJ1bMSerj1D2OVAb2WcgpQnG2a6kfc%3D&h=802b1b22\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://cpc.people.com.cn/n1/2020/0110/c64387-31542997.html</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9LKPGY9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9LKPGY9.jpg&h=76534a04&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZbBZjLQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZbBZjLQ.jpg&h=ef8bf1f6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2576f84db229c8372f6683f1550eafa22ca8cfcc","tid":1824046,"uid":6845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T07:09:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8e011ff65547c667e9ef3be3becf62e16b1d6c6","tid":1824046,"uid":153505,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T07:14:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vxk7tGb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fvxk7tGb.jpg&h=28ea99b1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e2109ab755bdc09f4d1e43b2a8431fbe358cbd53","tid":1824046,"uid